  "text": "Using the Miranda-Talenti estimate in Lemma 1.1, Lemma 2.2 and the Lax-Milgram Lemma, it is readily seen that there exists a unique strong solution to (2.4) under the Cordes condition (2.2). The proof is given in [22, p. 256 ], see also [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
